{"tid":2047373,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇書好中意間書同jot notes，有冇咩apps/device值得推介？","createTime":"2020-06-02T05:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T07:55:10.000Z","uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9fa2cb2ca86e9f2a72e29618429e2de37f5d24ee","tid":2047373,"uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:13:58.000Z","msg":"無論係教科書定小說<br />\n平時睇實體書好中意間書<br />\n或是係周圍既白邊寫筆記<br />\n畫到本書五顏六色<br />\n因為覺得咁樣易入腦d<br />\n同埋重溫番既時候方便d<br />\n<br />\n相反如果係圖書館借書或者睇網上既文<br />\n冇得比我好方便咁highlight/寫remarks<br />\n睇完都係白雪雪<br />\n會感覺好唔舒服<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打可以推介下d apps/device？<br />\n可以比我方便自如地間書/寫comments<br />\n如果好似小畫家咁自由就正<br />\n同埋唔知kindle可唔可以自由畫書<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e195e160df057479d4de7e638b2111b0df4a0beb","tid":2047373,"uid":58254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:23:09.000Z","msg":"marginal note??"},{"pid":"6096c5d5dc63d236754ee3ad6d6efae531a74d4f","tid":2047373,"uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e195e160df057479d4de7e638b2111b0df4a0beb","tid":2047373,"uid":58254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:23:09.000Z","msg":"marginal note??"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:34:11.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"93788a112f27042a4790bbfc292d448dab159923","tid":2047373,"uid":86828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:35:18.000Z","msg":"ipad + goodnote 5/ notability <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1501cd51c91eb38f32c092b3c2f3586358dac0d7","tid":2047373,"uid":58254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:56:36.000Z","msg":"apple store margin note"},{"pid":"bfd2a4b10ddfd9fbb9dcd8dbebc2ae23